363
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,210
I can swear to you.

364
00:23:36,890 --> 00:23:37,720
I can swear it on my life.

365
00:23:38,970 --> 00:23:39,880
Feng Huanan,

366
00:23:42,730 --> 00:23:44,570
