384
00:24:56,770 --> 00:24:58,560
how much suffering we've gone through!

385
00:24:58,950 --> 00:25:00,670
Because since you were born,

386
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,560
you've been standing

387
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,570
at the finish line that's impossible for us to reach!

388
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,240
