390
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:14,840
that I married you

391
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:16,450
for your family's money

392
00:25:16,450 --> 00:25:17,450
and resources.

393
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:18,970
