are you saying

400
00:25:44,170 --> 00:25:45,880
that everything

401
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,160
has a price to you?

402
00:25:48,750 --> 00:25:49,360
Yes.

403
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:51,250
Everything

404
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,530
has a price.

405
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,880
