419
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,490
are the happiest.

420
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,690
Let them laugh if they want to.

421
00:27:00,090 --> 00:27:01,120
I don't care.

422
00:27:01,650 --> 00:27:04,480
When I saw you in your wedding dress,

423
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:07,360
I thought you were so beautiful.

424
00:27:08,930 --> 00:27:10,280
At that moment, I felt that

425
00:27:11,390 --> 00:27:12,940
you had really grown up.

426
00:27:14,120 --> 00:27:16,050
But now, with you lying here,

427
00:27:16,050 --> 00:27:17,250
I feel like

428
00:27:17,250 --> 00:27:18,720
