464
00:29:06,090 --> 00:29:07,000
What's the point?

465
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,170
Come on, Mom.

466
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,940
I know what I want.

467
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:12,600
I want you to be here, and I want Doudou to be here.

468
00:29:12,890 --> 00:29:14,690
You said Doudou needs you.

469
00:29:15,900 --> 00:29:17,650
But is it really that Doudou needs you,

470
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:20,520
or are you using Doudou to prove you're needed?

471
00:29:23,290 --> 00:29:24,530
You just told me

472
00:29:25,130 --> 00:29:26,320
that seven years later,

473
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,440
you experienced failure in life.

474
00:29:29,530 --> 00:29:30,850
You lost your career,

475
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,490
your husband,

476
00:29:32,810 --> 00:29:34,250
and your friends.

477
00:29:34,490 --> 00:29:36,130
But you didn't lose them.

478
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:38,160
You lost yourself.

479
00:29:39,850 --> 00:29:41,450
Don't live in such an exhausting way.

480
00:29:42,490 --> 00:29:44,880
You need to learn to live in the moment.

481
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:45,810
Mom,

482
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:48,240
if it were you

483
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:50,040
who had a chance

484
00:29:50,040 --> 00:29:50,970
to go back to the past

485
00:29:50,970 --> 00:29:52,090
and change something,

486
00:29:53,790 --> 00:29:55,780
