487
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:57,970
For example, to see Dad again?

488
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,420
I would think about it.

489
00:30:02,850 --> 00:30:04,730
But if he were to

490
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,440
mess up other people's lives after he came back,

491
00:30:08,350 --> 00:30:09,430
I wouldn't.

492
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:13,120
Everyone is just a fleeting visitor

493
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,480
in other people's lives.

494
00:30:15,360 --> 00:30:16,880
Sooner or later, they will leave.

495
00:30:17,460 --> 00:30:20,500
Your dad will leave, your mom will leave,

496
00:30:21,170 --> 00:30:22,540
and your children will leave.

497
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:24,280
In the end,

498
00:30:24,850 --> 00:30:27,360
the only one left with you will be yourself.

499
00:30:27,540 --> 00:30:30,180
You should find yourself,

500
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:32,640
love yourself,

501
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:36,160
and cherish those who love you.

502
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:37,730
This is more important than anything else.

503
00:30:39,320 --> 00:30:41,250
Should I really give up on Doudou?

504
00:30:41,520 --> 00:30:43,280
Children are the fruit of love,

505
00:30:44,330 --> 00:30:46,240
not products of exchange.

506
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:48,240
You've always

507
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:49,580
understood this.

508
00:30:50,520 --> 00:30:51,320
Otherwise,

509
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:54,010
you wouldn't have come back from Feng Huanan.

510
00:30:55,570 --> 00:30:57,570
You need to respect your heart,

511
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,920
hold on to what's in front of you,

512
00:31:00,730 --> 00:31:02,520
and stop dwelling on the past.

513
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:03,640
Understand?

514
00:31:10,250 --> 00:31:12,130
Mom, then you...

515
00:31:14,060 --> 00:31:16,970
I'll face my life myself.

516
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,450
Just take care of yourself.
